item.title: We Live Our Truth
item.description: The Punisher: Season Two. We discuss when we saw the show, almost happy, where he ends up, two too many plots, muddled morality, the cast, the action and the violence, Frank changes and our ratings. Feed: https://the602club.libsyn.com/rss

item.title: WILOSOPHY: Troy Kinne - "Go With Your Gut"
item.description:
Strong recommendation to watch Troy's new series pilot, FULL STORY before listening to this ep. Troy goes deep on how he made it, including the stellar cast and crew he put together, how he self-funded it, and what lead him to take it on. Also: why Troy was literally “made the wrong way around”, the influence of John Edwards, and his secret writing/fitness camps.
